{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/Final_SteamPage_Title_01.png?t=1734292973\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/Final_Steam_Gif_01.gif?t=1734292973\" /><br>Honji has been accepted to the most prestigious college in the world. To get an edge, he is spending his summer in Kamanori. It's a small town famous for being permanently snowy, and award-winning prep courses. Hopefully nothing goes wrong.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/Final_SteamPage_Title_02.png?t=1734292973\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/Final_Steam_Gif_03.gif?t=1734292973\" /><br>With plans to just put his head down and study, Honji is taken by surprise with all of the colorful and interesting people he meets.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/Final_SteamPage_Title_03.png?t=1734292973\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/Final_Steam_Gif_02.gif?t=1734292973\" /><br>Through your choices, you will guide Honji along his path in Kamanori. But BE WARNED, choices are frequent and will have impact on your relationships.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/Final_SteamPage_Title_04.png?t=1734292973\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191370/extras/Final_Steam_Gif_04.gif?t=1734292973\" /><br>In addition to your choices, minigames will often pop up and help you gain favor with the people you meet.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asse